<lb n="0561c22" ed="X"/><lb n="0098a15" ed="R124"/><p xml:id="pX71p0561c2201">闐<note place="inline">徒堅切</note>　吽<note place="inline">許今切</note>　潰<note place="inline">胡對切</note>　眨<note place="inline">仄洽切</note>　豌<note place="inline">於丸切</note>　謼<note place="inline">荒烏切</note>　砒
<lb n="0561c23" ed="X"/><lb n="0098a16" ed="R124"/><note place="inline">扶迷切</note>　淈<note place="inline">古沒切</note>　<g ref="#CB05272"/><note place="inline">□□□</note>　齪<note place="inline">叉渥切</note>　噩<note place="inline">吾各切</note>　褫<note place="inline">直知切</note>　垃<note place="inline">力合
<lb n="0561c24" ed="X"/><lb n="0098a17" ed="R124"/>切</note>　圾<note place="inline">渠劫切</note>　磊<note place="inline">力罪切</note></p></cb:div>
